Package com.ey.challenge.gt.reader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileReader
    This class transforms a file path into a stream of raw data.
    Reader
    A root class for readers.
    ResourceReader
    A class that converts a resource name into a stream of lines.
    VisitsFileReader
    This class opens a given file, reads its content and returns a stream of visit periods.
    VisitsReader
    This is an abstract class of readers that process the name of a resource/file/etc. into a stream of significant (i.e. non-null) visit periods.
    VisitsResourceReader
    A concrete class that reads the data from resources.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ReaderException
    An exception thrown on file reading error.
